biocode.fims.bcid

Class BcidMinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • biocode.fims.bcid.BcidEncoder
      • biocode.fims.bcid.BcidMinter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Encoder

    public class BcidMinter
extends BcidEncoder
    This class mints shoulders for use in the EZID systems known as data groups. Minting data groups are important in establishing the ownership of particular data elements.
